{"type": "article", "id": 23872, "title": "渔衣面料制作的背包", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-15T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114940ypc7tkqHDzQOVMNJ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款背包来自一个叫未行的团队，他们从渔夫的下水服的材料中获得灵感设计。背包的形状近似一个旅行箱，很方正，可以完全摊开使用。渔衣面料有着舒适的触感，除了防水耐磨外还有明亮的色泽。这款包命名为 CityShuttle“都市穿梭”，可以适合旅行办公等多个功能。产品目前还没有上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114938bxVMunko32aYKwFL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114938tmParTBcQWowMEOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114939Q3shZzu8HPlmqcdX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071149394VaFGTvlJboUxqhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}